    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Branch of law that regulates the interrelationships of sovereign states and their rights and duties with regard to one another, in both peace and war.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
